subject: Tour of the Basque Country (Bicycle Race)
Bicycles and Bicycling
lead_paragraph: Ben Swift of England won the fifth stage of the Tour of Basque Country, finishing in Markina-Xemein, Spain, and Alberto Contador protected his 12-second lead ahead of the decisive time trial.
